            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="46.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="1. Starting the Game: Launch the game on your mobile device. You'll see your character standing on a platform." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
            <font>
               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="111.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="2. Objective: The goal is to move your character across various platforms at different distances by creating sticks of the correct length." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
            <font>
               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="177.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="3. Creating Sticks: Tap and hold on the screen to grow a stick. The stick will elongate vertically. The longer you press and hold, the longer the stick becomes." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
            <font>
               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="254.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="4. Releasing the Stick: Release your finger from the screen to place the stick. The stick will fall over to span the gap between the platform your character is standing on and the next platform." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
            <font>
               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="337.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="5. Crossing Platforms: If your stick is the correct length, your character will walk across it to the next platform." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
            <font>
               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="380.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="6. Scoring Points: You score points for every successful platform crossing. The game becomes more challenging as you progress, with varying distances between platforms." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
            <font>
               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="447.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="7. End of the Game: The game ends if your stick is too short or too long, causing your character to fall. Your final score is the number of platforms you successfully crossed." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
