               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="515.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="8. Retry: You can always start a new game immediately after failing to try and beat your high score." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
